1
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:30,100
=Fights Break Sphere=

2
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:32,800
=Episode 34=

3
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:37,800
You've grown so big.

4
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:43,100
My daughter has grown so big.

5
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:51,600
You haven't seen me in so many years,

6
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:53,700
of course, I've grown up.

7
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:10,300
When I heard about Xiao Yan’s matter.
I immediately rushed over to see you.

8
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:14,590
The matter of burning down the Fight Technique Pavillion
wasn’t caused by Brother Xiao Yan.

9
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:18,300
Uncle, don’t believe the rumors you hear from outsiders.

10
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,700
He and I are doing very well here.

11
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:25,100
Thank you, Uncle, for caring.

12
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:30,400
I want to take you back home.

13
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:33,500
When I left the Xiao family,
I already said,

14
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:37,000
if Brother Xiao Yan won't go home,
I won't go home either.

15
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:40,800
We’re not going back to the Xiao family.
We’re going back to Dragon Island.

16
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:46,400
Dragon Island is very unstable now.

17
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:49,790
The Dragon Mother has been missing for a year.

18
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:55,600
The remaining three Dragon Masters suspect
that your grandfather killed the Dragon Mother.

19
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:59,200
The soldiers of the three Dragon Master families
are going to attack us.

20
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:04,200
Your grandfather said to invite you back.

21
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:08,100
We want to establish a new Dragon Mother.

22
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:14,000
Uncle...

23
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:18,100
I can't go back anymore.

24
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:25,670
My surname is Xiao.
I grew up in Wu Tan City since childhood.

25
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,500
Could it be you've forgotten?

26
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:39,340
It was you
who personally delivered me to the Xiao family.

27
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:52,400
I don't remember one bit of the Gu family matters.

28
00:03:53,970 --> 00:03:57,140
I also don't want to go back
to be some kind of Dragon Mother.

29
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,800
Go back and tell them

30
00:04:01,610 --> 00:04:04,540
that the girl, named Gu Xun'er,

31
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,900
is already dead.

32
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,400
Whether you want to be or not,

33
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,800
you are a Gu Clan person!

34
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:20,750
I came here precisely to take you back.

35
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:30,800
Xiao Xun'er is Gu Xun'er.

36
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,200
Go back, all right?

37
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:38,600
I'm your father.

38
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,800
Leave!

39
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:51,200
When you originally abandoned me,

40
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:53,700
why didn’t you say that you were my father?

41
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,500
I hate you.

42
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,700
Xun'er!

43
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,200
Making you go and become the Xiao family’s daughter

44
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:45,200
was your grandfather’s idea.

45
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,800
Your mother and I didn’t approve.

46
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,800
I didn’t dare to come see you either.

47
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:55,200
I was afraid if I came,

48
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:58,200
I wouldn't be able to let you stay
in the Xiao family anymore.

49
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:04,400
I know that you’ve grown up.

50
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:07,800
I also know which friends you’ve made.

51
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:12,100
You took the entrance exam for the Jia Nan Academy.
You went to Yin City with Xiao Yan.

52
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:15,200
You returned to the Xiao family and came to this desert.

53
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:18,300
The Gu family spies brought all the news to us.

54
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:21,100
Your mother and I

55
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:25,100
memorized it all,

56
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:28,400
including your hairstyle,

57
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:31,600
what you wear and eat.

58
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:34,200
We know all of it.

59
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:52,400
If you hate, just hate this family.

60
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:55,200
Being an ordinary person in this desert,

61
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:58,100
life will be better.

62
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:22,300
Don't cry. Don't cry.

63
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:35,400
Daughter.

64
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:37,200
Father.

65
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,300
Brother Xiao Yan.

66
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,000
Uncle.

67
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,500
All of you must go back, right?

68
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:26,800
A small matter has occurred at home.
They want me to make a journey back.

69
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:29,500
Once it’s done, I’ll ride a horse
and come to find you right away.

70
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:34,250
Wait for me, Brother Xiao Yan.

71
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,100
Do you need any help?

72
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:43,799
No. It's just several elders making noisy complaints.

73
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:46,800
It'll be peaceful right away once Xun'er returns.

74
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:49,800
When it’s time, I’ll come to get you
and we'll return together to Dragon Island

75
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:53,600
to see your mother's childhood hometown.

76
00:08:55,810 --> 00:08:57,270
We're leaving.

77
00:09:08,830 --> 00:09:13,000
Walk us only to here, all right?
We'll see you again very soon.

78
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,000
Have a safe journey.

79
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,200
Let's go.

80
00:09:47,970 --> 00:09:50,150
Don't be upset.

81
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,800
After you’re done handling the matters at home,

82
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:55,100
send a pigeon with a message to me.

83
00:10:10,010 --> 00:10:11,990
Keep this with you.

84
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:20,860
This is the Dragon Clan’s pearl necklace.
It’s also my life’s pearl.

85
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:26,020
Seeing it is just like seeing me.

86
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,380
Be careful on the road.

87
00:11:47,730 --> 00:11:49,350
Second Brother.

88
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:53,290
Were you drinking wine?

89
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:57,860
I drank a little, but I threw it all up.

90
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:02,970
After Xun'er returns,
the matters of Dragon Island should be resolved.

91
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:10,080
Still, I can't stop worrying.

92
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:16,400
Then your father's marriage arrangement between you
and Xun'er, you even pushed that onto others.

93
00:12:21,430 --> 00:12:24,630
Impressive. You know everything.

94
00:12:37,570 --> 00:12:39,090
Let's go.

95
00:12:54,450 --> 00:12:56,120
Where are you going?

96
00:13:07,430 --> 00:13:08,960
Go in.

97
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:43,080
Kneel.

98
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:04,250
Twelve years ago, your Second Brother
and I accepted orders from Clan Leader

99
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:08,360
to come to Ta Ge'er Desert
to create a Xiao family branch.

100
00:14:10,310 --> 00:14:13,220
This year is the first time its master has come here.

101
00:14:15,860 --> 00:14:19,030
Xiao Yan, this is your good fortune.

102
00:14:20,990 --> 00:14:23,120
It's your responsibility.

103
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:30,780
What does this mean?

104
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:34,800
Come.

105
00:14:41,890 --> 00:14:44,220
Don’t you want to know the answer?

106
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:51,250
Everything you want to know is in here.
All the answers are inside.

107
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:55,880
The answers are inside there.

108
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:07,120
Yes, but the price is very big.

109
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:14,310
What's the price?

110
00:15:14,310 --> 00:15:19,000
Clan Leader said that if you die underground,

111
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:26,720
a new generation of the Xiao family
will not enter here again.

112
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:29,210
This place will then be sealed forever.

113
00:15:35,690 --> 00:15:38,370
Take care, Brother.

114
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,990
Good luck.

115
00:15:50,650 --> 00:15:52,650
You two aren't going in?

116
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:55,410
Big Brother! Second Brother!

117
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:55,150
[Xiao]

118
00:16:57,040 --> 00:16:59,690
The Fight Technique Pavilion of the Xiao family.

119
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:06,530
Clan Leader said you must go
from the first floor down to the fifth floor.

120
00:17:06,530 --> 00:17:12,150
Inside on the fifth floor,
there’s an ancestor of the Xiao family.

121
00:17:12,150 --> 00:17:16,060
You must pay your respects to him
in order to qualify to return.

122
00:17:24,460 --> 00:17:26,770
There's no seal on it at all.

123
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:31,650
[Xiao Manor]

124
00:17:41,390 --> 00:17:47,150
Just randomly killing people in broad daylight.
What other reasons can you speak of?

125
00:17:47,150 --> 00:17:51,920
What Five Great Clans?
What lifetime Oath of Allegiance?

126
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:55,300
In my opinion, everything is lost!

127
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:57,600
Even a carrier pigeon can't fly out of Wu Tan City.

128
00:17:57,600 --> 00:18:00,290
How about we find some good fighters?

129
00:18:00,290 --> 00:18:03,860
Twenty or thirty. We can all charge out together.

130
00:18:03,860 --> 00:18:08,890
What? You want to take one
or two hundred men and charge out there?

131
00:18:08,890 --> 00:18:11,170
That's just asking them to hasten to their deaths faster.

132
00:18:11,170 --> 00:18:14,480
Right now, we can't even see the faces of our enemies.

133
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:17,350
Even if the Xiao family is no longer
what it was,

134
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:20,090
we can’t let them bully us.

135
00:18:20,090 --> 00:18:22,090
Clan Leader, say the word.

136
00:18:22,090 --> 00:18:25,350
Although our Fight Qi isn’t high,
we still have dignity.

137
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:26,200
That's right.

138
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:29,590
No way can we let others laugh at us.

139
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:32,530
On the 9th of September, the demon visits.

140
00:18:32,530 --> 00:18:35,480
All the children of the Xiao family will enter the grave.

141
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:37,980
Selling coffins!

142
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:46,430
May I ask who is the elder that has a misunderstanding
with the Xiao Family? Please explain it to us.

143
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:51,600
[Heaven and Earth Fight Qi]

144
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:55,830
Clan Leader Xiao, do you want to buy some coffins?

145
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:59,560
I heard you are doing business here.

146
00:19:02,990 --> 00:19:06,740
May I ask, what is your name?

147
00:19:07,530 --> 00:19:12,500
With your Fight Qi, you don't rate
high enough to even ask me for my name.

148
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:19,610
Fifteen.

149
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,950
Twenty.

150
00:19:26,250 --> 00:19:32,000
I really don't have that many coffins.
Sorry about this.

151
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:36,920
Two people can share one. How does that sound?

152
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:38,720
Take this!

153
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:45,310
You--

154
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:50,650
Yin and Yang Sword inside the sleeve.

155
00:19:52,980 --> 00:19:57,090
Which one of the Thirteen Hall Elders
of the Cloud Mist Sect are you?

156
00:19:57,090 --> 00:20:00,000
Xiao Zhan was disrespectful.

157
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:02,620
At least you're not blind.

158
00:20:02,620 --> 00:20:05,750
You also know about the Thirteen Hall Elders
of the Cloud Mist Sect.

159
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:08,410
The Cloud Mist Sect's thirteen sets
of the Spirit Sword techniques

160
00:20:08,410 --> 00:20:11,520
were left to the Thirteen Hall Elders
to practice cultivation and refinement.

161
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:13,440
They haven't appeared in the Jianghu world for a century.

162
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:19,140
How did we offend you to the point
that you want to kill all our people?

163
00:20:21,340 --> 00:20:23,860
I’m Breaker of Clouds.

164
00:20:23,860 --> 00:20:29,250
Your Xiao family killed both of my disciples in front of
their tavern door. How do you explain this?

165
00:20:29,250 --> 00:20:32,970
They spied on my Xiao family secrets

166
00:20:32,970 --> 00:20:35,700
and murdered my Xiao family disciples.

167
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:38,290
The Cloud Mist Sect and the Xiao family
have been on good terms for centuries.

168
00:20:38,290 --> 00:20:43,080
I didn’t want, because of a few crazy attacks,
to break our alliance relationship.

169
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:46,230
It was secretly done out of respect for everyone.

170
00:20:46,230 --> 00:20:49,580
Since you have asked, that’s fine, too.

171
00:20:49,580 --> 00:20:52,010
The murderer is Xiao Zhan.

172
00:20:52,010 --> 00:20:55,240
Elder, please strike me.
It's just that

173
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:58,640
you absolutely mustn't injure my Xiao family disciples.

174
00:21:01,410 --> 00:21:04,050
You're nothing but a cripple.

175
00:21:04,050 --> 00:21:07,410
If I kill you, people will laugh at me.

176
00:21:07,410 --> 00:21:10,840
I want to kill all of the Xiao Family,
from old to young, everyone.

177
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:14,270
Only then will my heart be content.

178
00:21:14,270 --> 00:21:18,270
Just wait, slowly wait.
Don't get anxious about dying.

179
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:20,360
You're too much of a savage!

180
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:33,450
Endless sorrow and great danger.

181
00:21:33,450 --> 00:21:37,640
Beautiful city will be filled with blood.

182
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:43,150
The redness will end and the blood will disappear.

183
00:21:43,150 --> 00:21:45,870
The right or wrong will become butterflies.

184
00:21:45,870 --> 00:21:50,060
Cloud Mist Sect!

185
00:21:50,910 --> 00:21:53,040
[Black]

186
00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:05,920
[Earth]

187
00:22:50,100 --> 00:22:54,350
Medicine Elder! Look, these books
are all Xiao family Fight Techniques.

188
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:58,060
What is going on?

189
00:23:07,810 --> 00:23:11,960
[Heaven]

190
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:38,380
Heaven Rank Fight Techniques!

191
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:28,010
This is the Ruler Technique of the Xiao family.
I tried it. It's really impressive.

192
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:08,590
Medicine Elder!

193
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:13,490
Medicine Elder, do you know what this is?

194
00:25:13,490 --> 00:25:16,420
Elder. Medicine Elder.

195
00:25:17,620 --> 00:25:20,100
- Medicine Elder, let me tell you, did you kno--
-You're so annoying!

196
00:25:20,100 --> 00:25:23,000
Can't you take a rest? My head hurts already!

197
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:25,240
Do you know what this is?

198
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:28,230
How would I know?
The inside financial record of your family?

199
00:25:28,230 --> 00:25:32,590
I am telling you! It's the Flame Secrets!

200
00:25:33,330 --> 00:25:35,210
Flame Secrets!

201
00:25:35,210 --> 00:25:39,270
You said you had the only copy!
There's one more, right here!

202
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:45,620
This should be the copy your ancestor
copied from Star Fall Pavilion.

203
00:25:45,620 --> 00:25:48,210
But it can be a great comparison.

204
00:25:48,210 --> 00:25:52,970
Also, this and this. They are both Heaven Rank Fight Techniques.

205
00:25:52,970 --> 00:25:56,990
Let me tell you. This time, we struck gold!

206
00:25:57,630 --> 00:26:02,020
Good for the Xiao family! You spent so much
time to bring all the treasures here.

207
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:07,070
Though your father may have lost his Fight Qi,
he's still a big hero.

208
00:26:07,070 --> 00:26:10,860
I think you know the truth of the fire now?

209
00:26:12,610 --> 00:26:18,030
But why did my father have to
go to the extreme of casting me out?

210
00:26:18,030 --> 00:26:21,800
I guess it's because Darkness is coming
and he was afraid the Xiao family couldn't protect themselves.

211
00:26:21,800 --> 00:26:25,160
So he moved all the Techniques here first.

212
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:29,970
By expelling you and telling the world about it
is like leaving no offspring of his in this world.

213
00:26:29,970 --> 00:26:33,930
Xiao Zhan's thoughts and courage are really impressive.

214
00:26:33,930 --> 00:26:37,990
I can understand all this,
but the Xiao family is in danger.

215
00:26:37,990 --> 00:26:40,460
Shouldn't I stay with them?

216
00:26:40,460 --> 00:26:44,930
What kind of real danger? With what you're able to do now,
it won't make a difference.

217
00:26:44,930 --> 00:26:47,660
Your brother already told you
to go from Level 1 to Level 5.

218
00:26:47,660 --> 00:26:50,910
If you can't get out of here,
these will all be sealed up forever.

219
00:26:50,910 --> 00:26:53,100
My brother wants me to go from Level 1 to Level 5

220
00:26:53,100 --> 00:26:55,780
to visit an ancestor of the Xiao family.

221
00:26:55,780 --> 00:27:00,560
How do I do that? Is he still alive?

222
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:06,390
All you people from the Xiao family have a big problem.
You never speak clearly.

223
00:27:09,170 --> 00:27:12,190
From Level 1 to Level 5.

224
00:27:12,190 --> 00:27:15,720
Do I need to learn all these skills?

225
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:18,550
But isn't this too much?
How will I finish learning it all?

226
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:22,400
I don't know the answer to that question.
Your father left so many treasures to you.

227
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:27,010
That's your blessing. He pointed out the way.
You just practice.

228
00:27:32,460 --> 00:27:35,090
The Xiao Family will be fine, right?

229
00:27:35,090 --> 00:27:38,320
Rather than worrying about the clan,
you should worry about yourself.

230
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:42,240
Weren't you excited when you showed me these treasures?
Hurry up.

231
00:27:56,760 --> 00:28:02,600
Medicine Elder, recently, I really want

232
00:28:02,600 --> 00:28:07,400
to create some Fight Techniques
that belong just to myself.

233
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:24,600
This...

234
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:27,180
Clan Leader, what's going on?

235
00:28:27,180 --> 00:28:30,200
They are all my students.
They didn't have the guts

236
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:33,760
and tried to escape in secret.
They ended up getting killed.

237
00:28:33,760 --> 00:28:38,110
The bodies were still warm
when they were thrown over the doorway.

238
00:28:38,110 --> 00:28:43,210
It looks like the Thirteen Elders
have come all together.

239
00:28:43,210 --> 00:28:46,460
When they escaped, they told me.

240
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:49,770
I told them to walk together.

241
00:28:49,770 --> 00:28:53,620
I didn't expect this would eventually happen to them.

242
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:58,290
Clan Leader, you let them go.

243
00:28:59,280 --> 00:29:03,120
Since I can't protect them, why keep them here?

244
00:29:03,120 --> 00:29:07,590
Clan Leader, we can't damage
our ancestors' great reputation.

245
00:29:07,590 --> 00:29:09,620
We must fight to the death with our enemies.

246
00:29:09,620 --> 00:29:10,770
To the death!

247
00:29:10,770 --> 00:29:12,480
Yes! We'll fight them to the death!

248
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:16,820
Our ancestors' reputation is their business!

249
00:29:16,820 --> 00:29:21,710
The Xiao family has been here over a hundred years.
Do we have great talents?

250
00:29:21,710 --> 00:29:24,290
