277
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:48,680
Master, let me help you back to rest.

278
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:53,220
- You should go, too.
- Master.

279
00:31:58,510 --> 00:32:02,610
Master... please take care.

280
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:26,480
It's very quiet.

281
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:34,990
[Heaven]

282
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:56,190
[Xiao Manor]

283
00:34:06,170 --> 00:34:10,280
[Heaven and Earth Fight Qi]

284
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:37,000
What did I do to deserve this honor...

285
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:42,150
of meeting one of the Thirteen Elders
of the Cloud Mist Sect?

286
00:34:42,150 --> 00:34:47,820
All the ones who escaped from the Xiao Family last night:
men, women, old and young, a total of 133...

287
00:34:47,820 --> 00:34:49,530
are all dead.

288
00:34:50,370 --> 00:34:53,130
What should be done about their corpses?

289
00:34:54,409 --> 00:34:58,200
You think that the Xiao Family can't afford
to buy over a hundred coffins?

290
00:34:58,200 --> 00:34:59,970
What about you?

291
00:35:04,090 --> 00:35:10,620
The birds and insects will eat their bodies.

292
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:13,750
Do what you will.

293
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:23,830
Xiao Zhan, why is your
Fight Technique Pavillion empty?

294
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:32,200
If my family had good Fight Techniques,
we wouldn't have ended up in this position.

295
00:35:32,200 --> 00:35:35,360
