296
00:35:37,290 --> 00:35:39,390
Xiao Family...

297
00:35:41,050 --> 00:35:43,950
What's so great about the Xiao Family?

298
00:35:44,780 --> 00:35:49,820
A loser like you doesn't deserve to
be one of the Five Great Clans!

299
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:58,050
Hahahaha!

300
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:06,360
Again!

301
00:37:10,090 --> 00:37:12,280
Eight Extreme Collapse!

302
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:22,780
Sometimes it's Xiao family's Fight Techniques,

303
00:37:22,780 --> 00:37:26,060
sometimes it's Star Fall Pavillion's.

304
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:28,120
That's inappropriate.

305
00:37:38,580 --> 00:37:40,370
Who are you?

306
00:37:40,370 --> 00:37:43,270
Xiao Zhan left me a letter.

307
00:37:43,270 --> 00:37:48,430
He said you're the last child
in the Xiao family who has any talent.

308
00:37:48,430 --> 00:37:53,900
Looking at your messy skills, it's very disappointing.

309
00:37:57,820 --> 00:38:00,840
Xiao Yan greets the Ancestor!

310
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:03,990
