311
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:13,370
Ancestor! My big brother said in our family
there's still one ancestor whose soul was still here.

312
00:38:13,370 --> 00:38:17,580
Who would have thought
that you're still alive?

313
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:20,420
May I ask which Elder you are?

314
00:38:23,150 --> 00:38:27,960
You don't even know which elder I am;
and yet, you bowed to me?

315
00:38:30,860 --> 00:38:35,270
You're an amusing child.

316
00:38:37,110 --> 00:38:39,480
I am Xiao Zu.

317
00:38:40,650 --> 00:38:43,690
Xiao... Xiao Zu.

318
00:38:43,690 --> 00:38:45,900
